channel.title: Need Good Coder for Dedicated Server
channel.description:
I'm looking for a great coder to work for/with me. I know pretty much nothing about coding, but I'm aware that some individuals know a great deal about it. So I'm looking for anyone who's willing to work on my server, if you're good and you'd be available to help make the server great, then I'll put it on a dedicated host.
Add my msn if you're interested - leroux_b@hotmail.com
P.S - If you want more out of it, talk to me, we can agree on something.
